premise_source_doc_sentence: Sir Thomas Sean Connery KB  (  -LSB- ˈʃɔːn_ˈkɒnəri -RSB- born 25 August 1930  )  is a retired Scottish actor and producer who has won an Academy Award , two BAFTA Awards  (  one of them being a BAFTA Academy Fellowship Award  )  and three Golden Globes  (  including the Cecil B. DeMille Award and a Henrietta Award  )  .
